    "title": "Usage suggests Core has become less relevant than Knots",
    "body": "### Please describe the feature you'd like to see added.\n\n<img width=\"967\" height=\"466\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c7053cfa-3320-4378-8863-8cd2b7c69eec\" />\n\nFor some time now, my node is seeing significantly more Knots nodes than Core nodes. Could this be considered an issue if relevance is important?\n\nNote, my node favors nodes that provide transactions that make it into the mempool, so it's possible that other people are not seeing this unless their node also has this preference.\n",
